            "title": "港股開跌204點  阿里挫逾6%  網易飆一成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數競價時段開報23249點，跌204點或0.87% ; 恒生科技指開報5247點，跌50點或0.95% ; 恒生國企指數開報8431點，跌78點或0.92%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市現成交33.98億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"阿里巴巴官網圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230829-130621_20230810_FI_source-web_阿里巴巴-3_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"阿里巴巴官網圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230829-130621_20230810_FI_source-web_阿里巴巴-3_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">阿里巴巴官網圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)低開6.13%，報121元，為表現最差藍籌股，成交居第二位。集團季度收入遜預期。網易(09999)升10.87%，報186.4元，成交居第三位，為表現最佳藍籌股。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)跌2.07%，報132.6元。騰訊(00700)跌1.16%報509.5元，今除淨。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">赤峰黃金(06693)升3.09%，報25元。中國黃金國際(02099)首季虧轉盈，升3.94%，報54.1元。</p>\n</div>",
